77,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"其實我唔係好明<br />\n<br />\n有人寫定遺書上前線<br />\n有啲甚至自殺殉道<br />\n<br />\n你地明唔明你條命好寶貴架<br />\n你有咁嘅勇氣<br />\n應該要各方面upgrade 下自己<br />\n意識、體能、知識、戰術各方面都要提升<br />\n唔係係前線同班狗玩捉依因<br />\n最後被人撳低<br />\n畀人發洩暴打<br />\n再拉返去凌虐<br />\n成身傷、失去幾年自由同前程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56650cd01a23f04500e9ab05a68b9c76e0f82ba3","tid":1614280,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b061341411595b925b5c9eb17fea9c13f2a32b3","tid":1614280,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeb09ade31b9147206d418954ce0474227a94b2","tid":1614280,"uid":278881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解香港黑警會娼狂過外國咁多<br />\n甚至介癲話第三世界國家？<br />\n因為人地既反抗者真係會武力反抗<br />\n真係會全民武裝革命打內戰<br />\n黑警都係人<br />\n都儲怕死<br />\n所以外國既警察會識跟規矩玩<br />\n但香港呢？香港就係睇死香港人唔敢流血唔敢革命<br />\n咁咪比左膽佢地濫權瘋狂打壓示威囉"},{"pid":"bcb0de93961437da0807389bbe2ace29e16346ad","tid":1614280,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5941b20d88877e42efe55578fe95efe855f82df0","tid":1614280,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets